description: Selena's final live performance was recorded at the Houston Astrodome a month before her tragic death.
name: Selena Live: The Last Concert

review.name: fantastic
review.reviewBody:
This is Selena's best concert ever.I love when she sang the songs in the 70's.And i love when she's waving to her fans.She was such a great performer when you see her concerts.And her outfit was so pretty. She sang like 17 songs, and gave her all in every single one.She's better than most performers today.She sings with her heart and you could tell she really loved singing and entertaining.

She has such cool dance moves and seeing her dance makes me want to dance.She had so much energy and talent in her.She is truly a Tejano legend that will forever be remembered. I recommend this concert to all Selena fans.
